### 1. 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8080/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "imai",
    "password": "my_secure_password"
}

### 2. 用户登录 (获取 Token)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "imai",
    "password": "my_secure_password"
}

### 3. 测试图片上传
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

# REST Client 上传文件时要使用 multipart/form-data + < 文件路径
# 请把下面这个路径替换为你本机的图片文件路径
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< /Users/imaichika/Downloads/test.png
--WebAppBoundary--

# 成功后返回 JSON，里面会有 url 字段

### 4. 测试发布带封面和图片的文章
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
    "title": "测试图文混排",
    "author": "imai",
    "cover_image": "http://localhost:8080/uploads/<刚才生成的图片名>.jpg",
    "content": "这是一段文字。\n\n这是文章内插入的图片：\n![配图](http://localhost:8080/uploads/<另一张图片名>.png)\n\nMarkdown 就是这么简单！"
}

### 5. 验证拦截 (不带 Token 发帖)
# 预期结果: 401 Unauthorized
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "未授权的测试",
    "content": "这条内容不应该被存入数据库"
}

### 4. 创建文章 1
# @name createPost1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
    "title": "测试文章 1",
    "content": "这是第 1 篇测试文章。",
    "author": "imai"
}

### 5. 创建文章 2
# @name createPost2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
    "title": "测试文章 2",
    "content": "这是第 2 篇测试文章。",
    "author": "imai"
}

### 6. 创建文章 3
# @name createPost3
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "title": "新的文章",
  "content": "这是内容",
  "cover_image": "http://localhost:8080/uploads/xxx.png"
}


### 7. 分页测试 page=1&page_size=2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts?page=1&page_size=2
Accept: application/json

### 8. 分页测试 page=2&page_size=2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts?page=2&page_size=2
Accept: application/json

### 9. 删除文章 1
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts/{{createPost1.response.body.ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### 10. 删除后再次读取已删文章
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts/{{createPost1.response.body.ID}}
Accept: application/json


### 11. 测试图片上传 (png)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< /Users/imaichika/Downloads/test.png
--WebAppBoundary--


### 12. 测试文件上传 (其他)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< /Users/imaichika/Downloads/我的开题报告.doc
--WebAppBoundary--




